<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/604816-does-this-book-have-a-mysterious-story">does this book have a mysterious story behind it ?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_604816'><a id="like_count_community_question_604816" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/604816?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F14362.Bless_Me_Ultima">like</a></span>

